text: How is this ain't 10 or 20 million views already? Come on. Top-notch visuals. Consistent best-choreographed dance routine in their generation (for girl groups with 5 or more members). The expressions on their faces and even their body language tells the story of their song. You got to be PACKING kidding me. The transitions between choreographed formations are smooth like pancake syrup. Everyone from TWICE is doing their best because they are the LEGENDARY UNDERRATED INTERNATIONAL BEST 9-MEMBER GIRL GROUP and the NATION'S GIRL GROUP of their generation. Come on now. Choreographies for 9-member groups are generally difficult. The blocking, dance routine, body language, and transitions to sequential dance formations are 70% more difficult to optimally synchronize so that the choreography can be performed excellently, consistently, gracefully, and without mishaps. I started being a BLINK on July 26, 2019, and I became a ONCE on August 30, 2019, when I saw Jeongyeon with blue/turquoise hair wearing a cute headband in a concert/music show(?) on a tv I happen to lay my eyes upon. That's when I knew, I will make sure that the girl groups I loved and that are worthy of success will continue to prosper and get better as they continue their careers. #BlinkOnce ğŸ˜‰
